  - {fileID: 1735089002}
  - {fileID: 1070465871}
  - {fileID: 808459177}
  - {fileID: 2045289045}
  storyText: {fileID: 611830048}
  storyLines:
  - "N\u0103m 2085, m\u1ED9t t\xEDn hi\u1EC7u l\u1EA1 vang l\xEAn gi\u1EEFa \u0111\u1EA1i
    d\u01B0\u01A1ng \u2014 n\u01A1i ch\u01B0a t\u1EEBng c\xF3 con t\xE0u n\xE0o tr\u1EDF
    v\u1EC1."
  - "T\xEDn hi\u1EC7u \u1EA5y d\u1EABn \u0111\u1EBFn truy\u1EC1n thuy\u1EBFt Atlantis,
    th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 c\u1ED5 b\u1ECB ch\xF4n v\xF9i d\u01B0\u1EDBi l\xE0n n\u01B0\u1EDBc
    s\xE2u."
  - "B\xEAn d\u01B0\u1EDBi m\u1EB7t bi\u1EC3n y\xEAn b\xECnh l\xE0 san h\xF4, ng\u1ECDc
    trai, kho b\xE1u\u2026 v\xE0 nh\u1EEFng sinh v\u1EADt \u0111ang canh gi\u1EEF
    b\xED m\u1EADt."
  - "B\u1EA1n l\xE0 thuy\u1EC1n tr\u01B0\u1EDFng c\u1EE7a Ocean Explorer. H\xE3y
    l\u1EB7n xu\u1ED1ng, thu th\u1EADp kho b\xE1u v\xE0 kh\xE1m ph\xE1 s\u1EF1 th\u1EADt
    b\u1ECB l\xE3ng qu\xEAn."
  voiceSource: {fileID: 1298259810}
  storyVoices:
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: a19fc1febd04b8b468c2c334893f15fc, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 17d094806ea16ca48b17b37800f0847c, type: 3}
